  "short_description": "《X.A.O.C》is set in a world of exotic mythologies and legends -- the hundreds of characters who populate this universe, are a fusion of Taiwan, Vietnam, Thailand and Ryukyu cultures, resulting in an epic Oriental fantasy adventure.",
