  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/614860/extras/8272f7bf5571929b982f689ed997f5d2.poster.avif?t=1586921512\" width=616 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/614860/extras/8272f7bf5571929b982f689ed997f5d2.webm?t=1586921512\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/614860/extras/8272f7bf5571929b982f689ed997f5d2.mp4?t=1586921512\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><i>Attention!! The divinities and devils, the factions and ideologies of this world are so complex and intricate, the resulting text script of this game has over 4 million words. It is not an easy task to localize such a game into English, for the moment, it will only be possible to translate the UI and certain reference materials. The production team would like to apologize to all non-Chinese players around the world.</i><br><br><strong>【Weekly Maintenance Schedule】</strong><br>Maintenance will be on every Wednesday, 17:00 - 21:00 (PDT) , for a duration of 2 hours.<br>Thank you for your cooperation, and we apologize for the inconvenience.<br><br><strong>✭✭✭✭✭ 我們未必出類拔萃，但肯定與眾不同 ✭✭✭✭✭</strong><br><br>遊戲故事描述因「天律之災」的發生，導致過往的繁華在一夕之間消逝的世界，神、鬼、人之間界線不再分明的氛圍，而玩家在其中尋求救贖、探索生存之道－「律」。透過遊戲系統巧妙的引導，玩家將進入一個四處充滿異象，山崩地裂，百鬼夜行的世界。遊戲不再是打打殺殺為主要的目的，例如透過「超渡」死亡的怪物，玩家將感受萬物一體的禪意。雖然遊戲世界看似灰暗且生存環境惡劣，但遊戲裡仍有部分的人物充滿幽默感，他們將告訴我們的是，不論世界有多麼不美好，還是可以樂觀看待，並且幫助他人。<br><br>我們希望「X.A.O.C」能以饒富「禪意」的呈現玩的過程，才能讓玩家體驗到在過去玩遊戲時從未體驗過的感受，因此我們不按照舊的模式來製作，舊型式的遊戲格式似乎已經無法承載我們的初衷，我們希望遊戲需要很多充滿特色的內容。於是，我們用了數種特色玩法，去融入玩家的體驗當中！例如：溫泉、拜拜、泡茶、天燈、超渡、養役妖、觀落陰等系統，搭配電影手法般的劇情演出，而您就成為了戲裡的演員之一。 <br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/614860/extras/486c8adf47816aac2364887944640c92.poster.avif?t=1586921512\" width=616 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/614860/extras/486c8adf47816aac2364887944640c92.webm?t=1586921512\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/614860/extras/486c8adf47816aac2364887944640c92.mp4?t=1586921512\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >遊戲玩法</h2><br>✥ 多人連線、單機體驗。<br>✥ 兩大陣營(參番、穢犬)、四大種族(東道域、漠奔族、秧犬族、草奉族)。<br>✥ 五種體型(壯男、青女、蘿莉、巨漢、瘦男)。<br>✥ 7種職業，每種職業可裝備三種武器切換使用。<br>　▪ 百刃侍：華麗奇術快刀流<br>　▪ 斂罡斥：罡勁霸擊武鬥家<br>　▪ 弁天御：光與暗的代行者<br>　▪ 銃　宿：千里獨行器械師<br>　▪ 鬼兵將：狂氣鋼絕重甲兵<br>　▪ 談元客：曲奏和鳴元素使<br>　▪ 馭魂衛：鐵血燃魂狩魔士<br>✥ 獨創的「攻」、「速」、「破」連段觸發組合攻擊方式。<br>✥ 故事豐富的任務劇情(主線、支線、區域、每日、其他)。<br>✥ 探索存在於世界地圖中的世界王。<br>✥ 世界地圖中的數十個洞穴探索。<br>✥ 劇情、任務、活動副本高達數十個，難易度為「簡單、一般、困難、極限」。<br>✥ 公會系統、租界爭奪戰、攻城戰、競技場(PVP)。<br>✥ 職業武器進化升級，天賦專精點系統。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/614860/extras/d1938fe1d456beececa1f597e44dee22.poster.avif?t=1586921512\" width=616 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/614860/extras/d1938fe1d456beececa1f597e44dee22.webm?t=1586921512\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/614860/extras/d1938fe1d456beececa1f597e44dee22.mp4?t=1586921512\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >遊戲特色</h2><br>❂ 電影般手法的動畫劇情呈現。<br>❂ 祭拜、放天燈、泡溫泉、茶道、役妖(寵物)、超渡。<br>❂ 獨一無二的收藏櫃系統，每增加一項收藏品項，都能增強自身能力。<br>❂ 武器、防具、裝備附加能力的「兵識」系統。<br>❂ 締角系統：六象八屬、締角驅印、相生相剋。<br>❂ 熔爐系統：配方取得、材料利用、武器升級、裝備進化。<br>❂ 煉化技能：裁縫、鍛冶、工藝、鍊金。<br>❂ 成就系統：XAOC + Steam 雙成就，雙倍滿足。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/614860/extras/1c9c93ac700187f60bb035e29ffba4b5.poster.avif?t=1586921512\" width=616 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/614860/extras/1c9c93ac700187f60bb035e29ffba4b5.webm?t=1586921512\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/614860/extras/1c9c93ac700187f60bb035e29ffba4b5.mp4?t=1586921512\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></strong>",
